<title type="html"><![CDATA[7/4(Sat)10 Reasons why foreigners love Taiwan /  Youtuber's Influence On Society (Host: Mei)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=406&amp;p=423#p423"><![CDATA[
7/4(Sat)10 Reasons why foreigners love Taiwan /  Youtuber's Influence On Society (Host: Mei)<br /><br /><br />10 Reasons why foreigners love Taiwan<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://youtu.be/k9EsBuhMYo0">https://youtu.be/k9EsBuhMYo0</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion<br />1. There are more and more foreigners in Taiwan making videos on YouTube sharing their experience and love for Taiwan. Why do you think caused this trend?<br />2. Other than the 10 reasons  why foreigners love Taiwan listed in the video, can you think of any others?<br />3.there are many channels on YouTube made by foreigners in Taiwan. Have you subscribed to any and how is it?<br />4. What typical food or places in Taiwan would you recommend foreigners to try and explore?<br /><br /><br />Youtuber's Influence On Society<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://mynorsecode.com/2018/03/28/youtubes-influence-on-society/">http://mynorsecode.com/2018/03/28/youtu ... n-society/</a><!-- m --><br />Extra information:<br />Some of the most popular YouTubers make millions from their videos.<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.businessinsider.com/some-youtube-stars-make-millions-heres-how-you-can-make-money-too-2019-4">https://www.businessinsider.com/some-yo ... too-2019-4</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion<br />1. YouTube is now the most popular platform among young people, with 85% of teenagers using it. Why do you think young people love to watch YouTube OR to be YouTubers?<br />2. In your opinion, how does YouTube influence our lives and society?<br />3. Do you dream to be an YouTuber? If so, what program would you want to make and why?<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=25764">Michelle Hsu</a> — Tue Jun 30, 2020 11:46 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
